      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 2\"><math alttext=\"U sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span> are equal. For each system, the pairings of spheres include one pair with same-sign charges and two pairs with opposite-sign charges.</p>",
