      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\"><span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 1\"><math alttext=\"U sub 1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>1</mn></msub></math></span></span> is higher than <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"U sub 2\"><math alttext=\"U sub 2\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><msub><mi>U</mi><mn>2</mn></msub></math></span></span>. It would take positive work to move a positive test charge from far away to Point <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"C\"><math alttext=\"C\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">C</mi></math></span></span> in System <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1\"><math alttext=\"1\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mn>1</mn></math></span></span>.</p>",
